openmediavault-autorip (1.0.2) stable; urgency=high

  * Add strict server-side validation for RPC setSettings parameters
    - Validate booleans, integers, language codes, and enum choices
    - Validate DVD device format (/dev/srN) and absolute tmp_dir path
    - Fail safely if configuration file cannot be written

 -- Yannick MONTFORT <yannick.montfort@gmail.com>  Mon, 04 May 2026 10:50:00 +0200

openmediavault-autorip (1.0.1) stable; urgency=high

  * Fix crash OMV on plugin load caused by namespaced constants in PHP
    - Use global constants \OMV_ROLE_ADMINISTRATOR and \OMV_NOTIFY_MODIFY
  * Harden RPC config loading when autorip.conf is missing/invalid

 -- Yannick MONTFORT <yannick.montfort@gmail.com>  Mon, 04 May 2026 10:30:00 +0200

openmediavault-autorip (1.0.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Version initiale du plugin OMV 7 AutoRip DVD
  * Détection automatique DVD via udev
  * Rip MKV via MakeMKV
  * Décryptage CSS via libdvdcss2 (clés VideoLAN automatiques)
  * Transfert automatique vers dossier partagé OMV
  * Interface Web OMV 7 (ExtJS / YAML workbench)
  * Service systemd autorip.service
  * RPC PHP OMV 7 (getSettings, setSettings, getLogs)

 -- Yannick MONTFORT <yannick.montfort@gmail.com>  Sun, 03 May 2026 22:00:00 +0200
